// Copy to tools.ts. The agent-specific wiring: the record mappings (search/enrich) that do what
// `reduck run` alone can't — fetch a source entity and persist it — plus the decider bound to this
// agent's config. The generic judgment engine (judge → persist one Decision) lives in src/decide.ts;
// single base scripts the agent runs with `reduck run reduck/<host>/<slug>` directly, no wrapper.
//
// One identity key throughout (the source's canonical URL). Every entity + pipeline row upserts on
// it, so a re-run converges instead of duplicating; the funnel is monotonic (an earlier stage
// no-ops once the entity has advanced past its target).

